headline: SE Labs Award Reinforces NetApp Status as the Most Secure Storage on the Planet
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., July 02, 2025--NetApp® (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today announced that it was recognized as a standout performer in cybersecurity in the SE LABS ® Awards 2025. NetApp won the 2025 SE Labs Award for Enterprise Data Protection, validating NetApp’s status as the most secure storage on the planet.
